  <brief_title>Establishment of Radiomics Database by Clinical Application of Multiparametric MRI Based on Incoherent Undersampling</brief_title>
  <official_title>Establishment of Radiomics Database by Clinical Application of Multiparametric MRI Including DCE-MRI Based on Incoherent Undersampling</official_title>
