  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to establish radiomics database for pancreas cancer from multiparametric MRI
      including DCE-MRI obtained by using incoherent undersampling and radial acquisition for
      clinical staging as well as quantitative analysis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
