    <intervention_name>multi-parametric MRI</intervention_name>
    <description>multiparametric MRI is performed in all patients, and the sequence includes dynamic contrast enhanced (DCE) MRI, diffusion weighted imaging (DWI), tissue maps, and MR cholangiography.</description>
